dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents Kenya's district administrative boundaries in 2003. These data were acquired from the Kenya Central Bureau of Statistics (CBS).This data was used in maps throughout Nature's Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being.
